        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Next, the modern-pop-important “seventh chords.” If the bottom three notes make a major triad and we add a major third on top, we get a major-seventh chord, symbol Cmaj7."
        }
      ]
