      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Seventh chords sound more contemporary and colourful than basic triads."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "There are many other intervallic recipes, but knowing major, minor, and their seventh versions is enough for now."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "For deeper exploration, see"
